Package: keyATM
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Keyword Assisted Topic Model
Description: An R implementation of Keyword assisted topic models. By providing topic models with a small number of keywords, researchers can use their substantive knowledge and obtain interpretable topics. The models can also incorporate covariates and time trends.
